 lives,"],[2970,3029,"remember?"],[3220,3308,"Besides,"],[3308,3500,"I find a man that can cook"],[3566,3645,"very sexy."],[3766,3841,"Oh, is that right?"],[4158,4245,"What happened to you?"],[4329,4433,"Did someone do this to you?"],[4558,4620,"It's nothing."],[4700,4925,"It's just my husband and his parents."],[5008,5095,"Don't worry about it."],[5650,5766,"Someone tried to hurt you."],[5866,5991,"Of course I'm worried about it."],[6395,6479,"Why don't you go clean up"],[6479,6545,"in the restroom?"],[6604,6700,"I have to handle something."],[6795,6883,"I'll find you later."],[8395,8475,"Uncle Cole."],[8475,8570,"My dear brother."],[8570,8658,"Please take a seat."],[8862,8925,"Do you have any wine?"],[9154,9212,"Oh,"],[9333,9475,"a clumsy maid broke the bottle"],[9475,9637,"that we picked out just for you."],[9687,9829,"But this one is just as good."],[12087,12195,"This is delicious."],[12512,12591,"You should all try some as well."]],"22":[[1172,1232,"Cole!"],[1288,1392,"You have a problem with this family?"],[1412,1540,"You can take it up with Dad in hell."],[1632,1732,"He's the one who disowned you,"],[1748,1808,"not us."],[1828,1920,"Shut up, Dad."],[1968,2076,"Don't piss off Uncle Cole."],[2112,2236,"We still need him to do business."],[2304,2408,"Well, I'm not hungry."],[2528,2656,"I'm going to be in Dad's study."],[2888,2940,"Yeah, so"],[2984,3084,"we can still talk business,"],[3084,3124,"right?"],[3184,3268,"Please, Uncle Cole."],[3380,3472,"You're pathetic."],[3592,3648,"If we had your"],[3648,3740,"grandfather's inheritance,"],[3776,3864,"we wouldn’t have to be that"],[3864,3996,"bastard’s punchbags."],[4088,4168,"You better make sure"],[4168,4292,"Elara gives us an heir soon,"],[4376,4540,"so we can get the old man's money."],[6164,6276,"What happened to meeting"],[6276,6332,"with your uncle?"],[6360,6420,"Shut up."],[6460,6576,"It's none of your business."],[6840,6960,"Someone tried to hurt you."],[7052,7164,"Of course I'm worried about it."],[7324,74